Description: 'camtrapdp' is the R interface to Camera Trap Data Package
  ('Camtrap DP', <https://camtrap-dp.tdwg.org>), a data exchange format for 
  camera trap data. It is designed to read, filter and convert data (including
  to Darwin Core) before further analysis in e.g. 'camtraptor' or 'camtrapR'.
